# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_FLIGHT_NOZZLE_POSITION

## Summary
Use this command to adjust the vertical flight nozzles position on the vulkan, this controls whether the vehicle is in vertical flight mode or not

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** plane
* **FLOAT** nozzleRatio
